      - 80
      - 81
      - 90
`}</code></pre>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "load-balancer-configuration"
    }}>{`Load Balancer configuration`}</h3>
    <p>{`所有负载均衡的配置项都被定义在`}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`rancher-compose.yml`}</inlineCode>{`的`}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`lb_config`}</inlineCode>{`字段中`}</p>
